criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  individuals with severe congenital hemophilia A and B;

          -  on continuous factor prophylaxis;

          -  must be registered on CBDR (iCHIP in BC)

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  a history of explicit and documented previous treatment tailoring based on
             pharmacokinetic profiling;

          -  another congenital or acquired bleeding disorders other than Hemophilia A or B;

          -  active inhibitors (> 5 Bethesda units) or currently undergoing immune tolerance
             induction.
